data.description: This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom, 2 car garage home is LIKE NEW, sits on 1.4 acres and its ANDOVER SCHOOLS! Walk through the front door to spacious open concept with awesome living room space that flows effortlessly into the kitchen dining areas. The kitchen is all completely remodeled with new cabinets, countertops, appliances and a .5 bathroom off the dining room. The main floor boasts of a massive master bedroom that features awesome closet space as well as an over-the-top master bathroom with walk-in shower, double sinks, and linen closet. The basement has a family room, 2 bedrooms, and a bathroom. When stepping out back you will find an amazing covered patio and a fenced in back yard! There isn’t a single spot in this home that hasn’t been touched. New items include: Roof, HVAC, appliances, water heater, septic tank, insulation, flooring, paint, & windows.
